            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Hd1e108">Rubrica 7</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De versutia dolo malo: seu malitia fraude et deceptione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#P"/>De versutia dolo malo / seu 
               <lb ed="#P"/>malitia fraude et deceptione capitulum 
               <lb ed="#P"/>vii:-:-:-:-:-
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>In leuitico. ca. xviiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e125">non mentie mini
               <lb ed="#P"/>necque decipiet unusquisque proximum suum</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Moises in deuteronomio. ca. xxv.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e139">non ha
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>bebis in sacculo diuersa pondera maius 
               <lb ed="#P"/>et minus / nec erit in domo tua modius 
               <lb ed="#P"/>maior aut minor / pondus habebis ius
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tum et verum / et modius equalis et verus 
               <lb ed="#P"/>erit tibi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Psalmista. psalmus. v.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e156">virum sanguinum / et 
               <lb ed="#P"/>dolosum abominabitur dominus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e162">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. ix. psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e164">Cuius maledictione os ple
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>num est / et amaritudine / et dolo sub lingua eius labor et dolor.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e178">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Salomon in prouerb. ca. viiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e182">Statera dolo
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>sa abhominatio apud deum est / et pondus 
               <lb ed="#P"/>equum voluntas eius / abhominabile est 
               <lb ed="#P"/>domino cor prauum / et voluntas eius in 
               <lb ed="#P"/>his qui simpliciter ambulant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e194">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. xii. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e196">Non inueniet fraudu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>lentus lucrum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e208">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem xvi. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e212">fallax obtemperat labiis 
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/>mendacibus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e202">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem xvi. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e204">vir versutus odiosus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Isaias xxii. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e221">vasa pessima sunt fraudu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>lenti</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e227">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Iesus filius sirach in ecclastico. ca. viiii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e231">Est qui nequiter se humiliat / et interiora 
               <lb ed="#P"/>eius plena sunt dolo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e239">
               OMITTED
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e249">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Tullius de officiis. libro. primo. ca. xviii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e253">totius iniustitie nulla capitalior est 
               <lb ed="#P"/>quam eorum qui cum maxime fallunt id agunt ut 
               <lb ed="#P"/>viri boni esse videantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e261">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem rethoricorum artis vereris libro. primo
               <lb ed="#P"/>ca. xii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e265">primo quidem decipi incommodum 
               <lb ed="#P"/>est iterum stultum tertum turpe.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e273">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem de natura deorum libro. iii. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e275">versu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tos eos appello quorum celeriter mens 
               <lb ed="#P"/>versatur. Calidos autem quorum tanquam ma
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>nus opere sicut animus usu concaluit
               <lb ed="#P"/>Malitia est versuta et fallax ratio nocendi</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e288">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ouiduis epistolarum epistola. iii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e292">Fallere credentem nulla est operosa pu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>ellam. Gloria.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e298">
               OMITTED
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e306">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem epistola. xii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e310">Tarda solet rebus magnis ines se fides</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e316">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem de arte amandi libro. primo.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e318">Parua leues capiunt animos
               <lb ed="#P"/>fallentes magna ex parte profaniom
               <lb ed="#P"/>Sunt genus in illaqueos quos posuere cadunt
               <lb ed="#P"/>Non enim<!--Large space here--> equior ulla est. 
               <lb ed="#P"/>Quam necis artifices arte perire sua.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e332">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem libro. iii. et fi:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e334">iudice me fraus 
               <lb ed="#P"/>est concesso repellere fraudem 
               <lb ed="#P"/>Arma possit<!--This word isn't in the original quote.--> in armatos sumere iura sinunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e344">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem defastis libro. iii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e346">Fraude perit virtus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e353">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Marcus in evangelisto. capitulo. vi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e357">lucerna copo
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>ris tui est oculus tuus ibi tenebrosum
               <lb ed="#P"/>et cetera</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e369">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem vii. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e371">attendite a falsis prophetis cetera</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e385">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Matheus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e389">non fraudem feceris.
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum libro. xiii.
               <lb ed="#P"/>epistola. vii.</ref> Malitia ipsa maximam par
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tem sui veneni bibit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e399">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem epistola. . et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e403">Quod loquimur 
               <lb ed="#P"/>sentiamus concordet sermo cum vita.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e409">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem declamationum seu ciuilium eorum
               <lb ed="#P"/>libro. vi. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e411">Circum scriptor 
               <lb ed="#P"/>semper crimen in specie legis inuoluit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e421">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Lex de dolo. li. i. ยง. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e425">labeo diffini
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>uit dolum esse omnem caliditatem falla
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>ciam machinationem ad circumueni
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>endum fallendum / decipiendum al
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>terum adhibita.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e436">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ti. pro socio. l. verum. ยง. hoc</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e440">quoque
               <lb ed="#P"/>non est equum dolum suum quemquam re
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>uelare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e448">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ti. del. ii. cum pater ยง. ante pe.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e450">Non videtur dolo facere qui fraudem 
               <lb ed="#P"/>excludit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e456">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ti. de Re. iur. l. infrcscripta /</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e460">nemo 
               <lb ed="#P"/>videtur fraudare eos qui sciunt / et consen
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tiunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e466">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Martialis chochus libro undique sus
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>cepto. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e470">inscrutabilis est male
               <lb ed="#P"/>fidei mentis abusis.</quote>
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Auctor libri de forumula honeste vite
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/>ca. ii.</ref> <quote>prudens falli non potest necque fal
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>lere vult</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e480">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Prosper sub. epigramate.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e484">Fallaces semper curis torquentur amaris. 
               <lb ed="#P"/>Et mala mens numquam gaudia semper habet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e492">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum libro viiii. epistola. xxiiii.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e496">Quelibet malitia formidat contra 
               <lb ed="#P"/>manifesta bona aliquid profiteri dum 
               <lb ed="#P"/>generalibus odiis veretur exponi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e507">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Gregorius in pastorali. ca. xxxvi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e511">Im
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>puri dum reprehendi metuunt semper 
               <lb ed="#P"/>improbas defensiones querunt / semper 
               <lb ed="#P"/>pauidis suspitionibus agitantur / nichil 
               <lb ed="#P"/>autem est ad defendendum puritate tutius
               <lb ed="#P"/>nichil ad dicendum facilius veri
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tate vide super.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e525">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Versificator fabularum exopi. fabula iii.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e529">Omne genus pestis superat mens dis
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>sona xbis. Cum sentes animi florida
               <lb ed="#P"/>lingua polit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e539">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem fabula. xx.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e541"><sic>Qi</sic> minus est tutu / retia iure subit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e547">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem fabula xxiiii.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e549">Si tibi quid detur cur detur respice sidas
               <lb ed="#P"/>Cui des ipse nota / teque gulose doma.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e561">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem fabula xxxii</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e565">Me decuit fraudem pellere fraude 
               <lb ed="#P"/>pari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e571">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem fabula/ xxxviiii..</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e575">Sordibus ibuti nequeunt dimittere sordes. 
               <lb ed="#P"/>Fallere qui didicit fallere seper auet</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e582">
               <pb ed="#P" n="50-v"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem fabula xlvi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e586">Fine malo claudi / mala vita meretur 
               <lb ed="#P"/>iniquus: Qua capit insontes se dolet 
               <lb ed="#P"/>arte capi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e594">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Auctor libri qui dicitur pamphilus. ca xxvi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e598">Nam dolus insidias tendit ubique suas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e604">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Auctor libri qui dicitur facetus. ca vii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e608">Fraude sed est enim calidus omnis homo.
               <lb ed="#P"/>Fallere fallentes nulla ratione vetatur.
               <lb ed="#P"/>Condecet ut fallax corruat arte sua.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e618">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Gualfedrus in poetria. ca. xviiii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e622">Lex est equa dolum referire dolore dolosum
               <lb ed="#P"/>In caput unde fuit egressus habere regressum</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e630">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Auctor libri dicitur astroboli.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e634">Fallere prudentes pellis omnia nequit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e640">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Bellinus in speculo vite. parte. primo. ex. ix.
               <lb ed="#P"/>et pe.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e644">Fallere fallentem de ratione potes.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-d1e651">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Prouerbium vulghare /</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d25707-Qd1e655">le buone parole 
               <lb ed="#P"/>et rei facti / in gannano esaui ematti.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
